        (CyberCore::Geolocation::GeoNotifier::startTimerIfNeeded): Renamed from startTimer. Starts the timer if a timeout was specified.
        (CyberCore::Geolocation::GeoNotifier::timerFired): Modified. Calls the error callback if specified, and reports the timeout to the Geolocation object.
